# ğŸ¾ Pet Adoption Platform

A simple Node.js + Express + MongoDB API to manage and browse adoptable pets.  
Built to demonstrate backend development, authentication, file uploads, and RESTful API design.

![Screenshot](./screenshot.png)

---

## âœ¨ Features

- View list of adoptable pets
- View single pet details
- Admin login & register (JWT-based authentication)
- Admin can:
  - Add new pets (with image upload)
  - Edit pet information
  - Delete pets
- Image uploads stored locally
- Filter or search pets by type, age (coming soon)

---

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- Multer (file upload)
- JWT (authentication)
- bcryptjs (password hashing)
- dotenv
- CORS

